Ashen — A Dark Souls III–inspired Dungeons & Dragons one-shot for Foundry VTT
=============================================================================

This is a personal, non-commercial fan project.

GAME RULES CONTENT
------------------
All Dungeons & Dragons mechanical content in this project is derived solely from
the System Reference Document 5.1 ("SRD 5.1") by Wizards of the Coast LLC, which
is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License
(https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/legalcode).

  "This work includes material from the System Reference Document 5.1 ('SRD 5.1')
   by Wizards of the Coast LLC and available at
   https://dnd.wizards.com/resources/systems-reference-document. The SRD 5.1 is
   licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License."

ORIGINAL CONTENT
----------------
The homebrew rules, stat blocks, encounter and level design, journal text, and
build tooling authored in this repository are original works "inspired by" the
Dark Souls series. They are released for personal use.

DARK SOULS III
--------------
Dark Souls III and all related names, characters, art, and assets are the property
of FromSoftware, Inc. and Bandai Namco Entertainment. This project ships NO
FromSoftware copyrighted text, art, audio, or assets. Names and concepts are used
in a transformative, non-commercial, fan-homage capacity only. This project is not
affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by FromSoftware or Bandai Namco.

ART & AUDIO
-----------
No FromSoftware art or audio is included. Battlemaps and tokens shipped here are
original/placeholder schematics; the DM supplies their own or sourced art and
licensed audio (see the curated free-source list in the module).
